Ashley Graham -LRB- born October 30 , 1987 -RRB- is an American model .
She has appeared on the cover of fashion magazines such as Vogue , Harper 's Bazaar , Glamour , and Elle .
In addition , she appeared in several Levi 's campaigns .
Graham has appeared on The Tonight Show with Jay Leno , Entertainment Tonight , and CBS News and was interviewed by NPR about plus-size modeling .
In 2016 , she became the first plus-size model to appear on the cover of the Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issue .
In 2017 , Graham became the first plus-size model to appear on the covers of British and American Vogue .